metadata.name: Cargo 1/1
metadata.description:
Secret cache of vinyl records, wide-eyed reverences, rose tinted glasses. Through T-shirts, tattoos, and time spent on message boards. Kinetic digital obscurity. Bold, retro, thick, round frame lavender lens tinted glasses. 

Synth Graph: a real life portrait photograph of a beautiful blonde haired tanned runway model posing in vintage 70s streetwear, television sunglasses and red lipstick, shot with a Canon 5D Mark IV, highly realistic, ultra detailed. Sampler: klms, steps: 70, scale: 10.
